<p>Este important de notat cÄƒ o componentÄƒ poate fi un element, dar nu È™i invers. IatÄƒ un exemplu concret:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// Aceasta este o componentÄƒ</span>
<span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">UserPage</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
